{"tid":1829134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個黃子華都要講咁耐 連登已死","createTime":"2020-01-18T12:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T17:48:02.000Z","uid":29994,"like":17,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1e4eaadc53431c8873f6853b75d99a5d415b65a8","tid":1829134,"uid":29994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:50:51.000Z","msg":"Loop返一次佢嘅棟篤笑就知佢點啦<br />\n一致對外呀手足<br />\n<br />\n反共嘅 就係手足<br />\n就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n子華神14年人人都唔敢出聲嘅時候<br />\n佢就出個棟篤笑<br />\n呢啲就唔記得<br />\n剩係係咁話人哋唔出聲<br />\n真係要學熱狗講返句 &quot;yellownazi&quot;<br />\n<br />\n出聲就黃 唔出聲就藍？人唔笑狗都吠<br />\n<br />\n子華神係黃係藍都可以討論咁耐<br />\n真係笑死我<br />\n套戲 好睇咪睇囉 唔好睇咪算囉<br />\n<br />\n最後 聽日見啦 手足們 唔好再嗌交啦<br />\n<br />\nPS 連唔發聲嘅自由都唔俾人嘅話 香港人真係未ready擁有民主"},{"pid":"80bc5e3d1cf435cb4a2ee097ed99414e5a0cc976","tid":1829134,"uid":268537,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jHpddE9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjHpddE9.png&h=838b65e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uq7m60b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUq7m60b.png&h=ce0a2de8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泛民法治未死要批鬥,投白票<br />\n食藍店要批鬥,影大頭<br />\n黃子華呢幾個月冇講嘢而家先表態要批鬥,罷睇佢戲<br />\n同一個風向嚟"},{"pid":"5f5456acf549a2d6a5f5dd0b6995dc46361dcd04","tid":1829134,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"好多風向狗"},{"pid":"ad82c46a1c1826068991fb4bd6b9e7b39ecdc2d2","tid":1829134,"uid":158889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T12:59:59.000Z","msg":"你地都唔搞清楚革命理念 點同你地行落去? <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f978bf83238ba2a8cfeb149d2be811d91622fc2d","tid":1829134,"uid":91017,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T13:03:24.000Z","msg":"因為達哥為左救港, JJ染左花柳, 所以要上連登谷人氣"},{"pid":"d3f185b19585f4351035ed33fc4984173055f20c","tid":1829134,"uid":268